<div class="info_margin_div room_description"> The Erbil Rotana Hotel is located in Erbil, overlooking the Sami Abdul Rahman Park, one of the largest parks in the Middle East. It features a pool, a wellness centre and 5 food and beverage outlets. It also offers free parking.

Equipped with 201 spacious rooms and suites, each air-conditioned unit at The Erbil Rotana is elegantly decorated. They all have a bathroom with a walk-in rain shower and a separate bath tub.

For lunch and dinner, the 5 on-site restaurants serves mesmerizing food adhering to all tastes and served by friendly, professional and efficient staff. The bar offers drinks and light snacks. A buffet breakfast is available daily upon request.

The sauna and the massages offered at Zen the spa allow guests to relax after a session in the world class fitness centre. An executive lounge is available for guests staying at the Club Rotana rooms. The hotel also provides 7 meeting rooms and event venues with the latest equipment upon request.

Conveniently located ten minutes away from Erbil International Airport and in the midst of the Fairground as well as business centers. The English and Italian villages are just a few minutes away by car. Erbil’s citadel is just 10 minutes’ drive away. 

We speak your language!<br>
